item.description:
 MySQL 连接报错  &ldquo;Host &lsquo;10.7.30.133&rsquo; is blocked because of many connection errors; unblock with &lsquo;mysqladmin flush-hosts&rsquo;&rdquo;
 解决方法 增加最大错误连接数 mysql&gt; use mysql; # 查看最大错误连接数 mysql&gt; show variables like '%max_connect_errors%' # 修改最大错误连接数 mysql&gt; set global max_connect_errors = 1000; # 查看修改结果 mysql&gt; show variables like '%max_connect_errors%'  重置计数器 mysql&gt; flush hosts;  或者
$ mysqladmin flush-hosts
